<section class="our-mission">
  <h1> Empowering Haiti's Youth </h1>

  <div class="values">
    <div class="value globalization">
      <div class="title"> Globalization</div>

      <div class="icon">
        <i class="fas fa-globe-americas"></i>
      </div>

      <div class="description">
        <p>
          We prepare our students with all the tools necessary to excel in
          the global community.<br><br>

          The trend toward the global economic village is clear, and the 21st
          century may very well become known as the century of the “global world”. <br><br>

          As a result, we provide stringent language training focusing on fluency and
          complete comprehension at writing and speaking English. All of our students
          have historicaly excelled at passing the TOEFL exam.<br><br>

          Not only through language, we have our students adopt a global mindset.
          They remain informed on the happenings in countries abroad and are educated on
          many foreign cultures.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="value business-savvy">
      <div class="title"> Business-Savvy</div>

      <div class="icon">
        <i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i>
      </div>

      <div class="description">
        <p>
          As of 2019, Haiti's GDP is $14.33 billion and ranked 149th in the world.<br><br>

          Putting political, economic, health, and disaster-related reasons aside; we must do better.<br><br>

          That is why we prepare our students for the world economy and foster a
          strong sense of entrepreneurship.<br><br>

          Our students are exposed to cutting edge technologies and educated at the
          art of capital investments. By practicing paper trading, analyzing tech
          industry & startup trends, and learning practical business administration, we equip our
          students with the tools to be both the founders of tomorrow and thrive in a corporate environment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="value leadership">
      <div class="title"> Leadership</div>

      <div class="icon">
        <%= inline_svg_tag('podium.svg') %>
      </div>

      <div class="description">
        <p>
          Leaders do not fall from trees, whole societies must prioritize their
          formation and Haiti is in a desperate need of new innovative, inspiring,
          creative and modern leaders!<br><br>

          We cultivate this trait in our students, so that they may become a greater
          next-generation of Haitian leadership.<br><br>

          We have participated in Future Business Leaders of America for 10 years running,
          as well ass the National Leadership Conference. Our students become skilled
          orators, effective communicators, and adept at planning & organization.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

